        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Announcing peace with Waco and Tahuacano chiefs.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><placeName>Nacogdoches </placeName><date when="1827-06-03">June the 3,&#8212;1827</date></p>
<p>Dear Sir</p>

<p>I am happy to inform you that <date when="1827-06-02">yesterday </date>I have maid Pease with
the <persName>Waco </persName><persName>Nesion </persName>and <persName>tawacanys </persName>also the <persName>chiefs of Both nasions
</persName>is now in this Plase you can treat them as <persName>friends </persName>and can let
your <placeName>uper setelment</placeName> now it <date when="1827-06-04">tomorrow </date>I shall start with them to
meet the <persName>Comanches </persName>and gow with them to <placeName>Sn. Antonio</placeName> to settel all in
this thare is nothing worth your notis to Right you    all is quiot</p>

<p><persName>Peter E. Bean </persName>   [Rubric]</p>
<p>[Addressed:] <persName>Sor Dn. Esteban F Austin</persName>&#8212;en <placeName>Sn fliipe&#8212;Brasos</placeName></p>


        </div1>
